---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Disclaimer | Harmonium Halt" description="Disclaimer for Harmonium Halt website. Information about educational content, affiliate links, and accuracy of musical information." noindex={false}>
  <div class="bg-white border-b border-ebony/8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-3 text-xs text-ebony/40">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-saffron-600">Home</a><span class="mx-2">›</span><span class="text-ebony/70">Disclaimer</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="font-display font-black text-3xl text-ebony mb-2">Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="text-ebony/50 text-sm mb-8">Last updated: December 10, 2024</p>
    <div class="prose-harmonium space-y-5 text-ebony/70 leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-6 mb-3">Educational Content</h2>
      <p>The content on Harmonium Halt is provided for educational and informational purposes only. While we strive for accuracy in our lessons and articles, music theory and practice methods can vary between traditions, teachers, and schools of thought. Our content represents one perspective based on widely accepted practices in Hindustani classical music.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">No Professional Music Instruction</h2>
      <p>Harmonium Halt is an online educational resource and does not replace personalized instruction from a qualified music teacher. For advanced classical study, examination preparation, or professional performance, we recommend seeking guidance from a qualified music guru or teacher.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Product Recommendations</h2>
      <p>Our buying guides and product recommendations are based on research and general knowledge. We may include affiliate links in some articles, which means we may earn a small commission if you purchase through our links, at no extra cost to you. We only recommend products we genuinely believe are suitable for learners.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Web Harmonium Accuracy</h2>
      <p>Our web harmonium uses the Web Audio API to generate sounds at mathematically correct frequencies. However, it is a digital simulation and does not perfectly replicate the acoustic qualities of a physical harmonium. It is intended as a practice and learning tool, not a performance instrument.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Health and Safety</h2>
      <p>When practicing any instrument, please ensure you use proper posture and take regular breaks to avoid repetitive strain injuries. If you experience pain while playing, stop and consult a healthcare professional.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about our content or this disclaimer, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@harmoniumhalt.com" class="text-saffron-600">hello@harmoniumhalt.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
